  "title": "Executive, Business Development",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description : </strong>Assist   with tender submission for yard repairs, fabrications, new building and   contractual matters.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities : </strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for marketing yards to local and overseas clients.</li>\n  <li>Able to engage global industry contacts and cultivate strong relations with clients.</li>\n  <li>Solicit and collate market intelligence for development of business strategy</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and work with internal cross-functional departments to work on quotations and support the execution and delivery of projects/ jobs.</li>\n  <li>Assist with tender submission</li>\n  <li>Maintain positive relationships with all existing and potential clients.</li>\n  <li>Prepare monthly marketing report on business negotiations, proposal and tender.</li>\n  <li>Assist with all contractual related matters.</li>\n  <li>Provide support in vessel chartering.</li>\n</ul>",
